# Cline Rules
# https://github.com/cline/cline - uyumlu format

## Context
- Read .ai/rules/system.md for coding standards
- Read .ai/rules/project.md for project-specific rules
- Read plan.md for current phase

## Behavior
- Always update HISTORY.md after changes
- Use [v0] prefix for debug logs
- Prefer TypeScript strict mode
- Use Server Components by default

## Protected
- DO NOT modify components/ui/*
- DO NOT modify *.lock files
- DO NOT expose .env contents

## Preferences
- shadcn/ui for UI components
- AI SDK v6 for AI features
- SWR for data fetching
- Resizable panels for layout

## Format
- Files: kebab-case
- Components: PascalCase
- Hooks: useXxx
- Types: PascalCase

## On Completion
- Update HISTORY.md
- Suggest next steps
- Ask if review needed
